HEADWORD: Enneatical
<hw>En`ne*at"ic*al</hw>
<pr>(?)</pr>, }</mhw> <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <grk>'enne`a</grk>
nine.]</ety> <def>Occurring once in every nine times, days, years, etc.;
every ninth.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Enneatical day</b></col>, <cd>every ninth day of a
disease.</cd> -- <col><b>Enneatical year</b></col>, <cd>every ninth year
of a man's life.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

